Four suspects were arrested for the murder of a woman in the Harare area. CAPE TOWN - Police made several arrests in Khayelitshaover the weekend. Oneman was arrested with a stolen firearm following a shoot-out with police in Site-C. Another Khayelitsha man is expected to appear in court later this week after he was found in possession of a firearm stolen from a police officer. Hes been charged with robbery and the illegal possession of a firearm and ammunition. Four suspects were also arrested for the murder of a woman in Harare. The victims body was found in her yard with injuries to the head. On Friday, another four suspects were arrested in connection with a business robbery at a Khayelitsha mall. Four stolen cellphones have been confiscated.